cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with inter-vehicle communication for autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the proposed approach involves fusing perceptual observations to augment perception performance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses a new runtime and evaluation framework for testing cooperative perception. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is mentioned in the paper as the trust modelling involves verifying the accuracy of reported object detections. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the paper proposes a novel approach for AVs to communicate and cooperate based on trust modelling.
